ic/24f34d699980ff1de69a6752efb2eb7b/c7900/IHOP-Gift-Card-Promo-TV-Graphic-1920x1080-1.jpg 222w,\n/static/24f34d699980ff1de69a6752efb2eb7b/125c9/IHOP-Gift-Card-Promo-TV-Graphic-1920x1080-1.jpg 445w,\n/static/24f34d699980ff1de69a6752efb2eb7b/78d8c/IHOP-Gift-Card-Promo-TV-Graphic-1920x1080-1.jpg 889w,\n/static/24f34d699980ff1de69a6752efb2eb7b/94590/IHOP-Gift-Card-Promo-TV-Graphic-1920x1080-1.jpg 1334w,\n/static/24f34d699980ff1de69a6752efb2eb7b/bd880/IHOP-Gift-Card-Promo-TV-Graphic-1920x1080-1.jpg 1778w,\n/static/24f34d699980ff1de69a6752efb2eb7b/69b48/IHOP-Gift-Card-Promo-TV-Graphic-1920x1080-1.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 889px) 100vw, 889px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 889px) 100vw, 889px\" srcset=\"/static/24f34d699980ff1de69a6752efb2eb7b/c7900/IHOP-Gift-Card-Promo-TV-Graphic-1920x1080-1.jpg 222w,\n/static/24f34d699980ff1de69a6752efb2eb7b/125c9/IHOP-Gift-Card-Promo-TV-Graphic-1920x1080-1.jpg 445w,\n/static/24f34d699980ff1de69a6752efb2eb7b/78d8c/IHOP-Gift-Card-Promo-TV-Graphic-1920x1080-1.jpg 889w,\n/static/24f34d699980ff1de69a6752efb2eb7b/94590/IHOP-Gift-Card-Promo-TV-Graphic-1920x1080-1.jpg 1334w,\n/static/24f34d699980ff1de69a6752efb2eb7b/bd880/IHOP-Gift-Card-Promo-TV-Graphic-1920x1080-1.jpg 1778w,\n/static/24f34d699980ff1de69a6752efb2eb7b/69b48/IHOP-Gift-Card-Promo-TV-Graphic-1920x1080-1.jpg 1920w\" src=\"/static/24f34d699980ff1de69a6752efb2eb7b/78d8c/IHOP-Gift-Card-Promo-TV-Graphic-1920x1080-1.jpg\" alt=\"IHOP Summer Fun Deal\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span><br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Today is the most exciting day of the summer!</h2>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://www.ihop.com/en\">IHOP</a> Summer Fun Deal with <a href=\"https://www.sixflags.com/fiestatexas\">Six Flags Fiesta Texas</a> is in full swing and we’re sure you can’t wait to get your hands on this amazing deal.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\nVisit any participating IHOP, and for just $79.99 you can get 4 tickets to Six Flags Fiesta Texas and a $40 gift card to IHOP.  That’s right, for just the price of one regular admission ticket to Fiesta Texas you get 4 tickets into the park AND a $40 gift card to IHOP. It’s an unbelievable deal and the perfect way to have the most fun filled summer. See store for details.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\nFuel up the family with a delicious breakfast at IHOP and then head over to Fiesta Texas to experience all the thrills the park has to offer. Be sure to experience the all new Thunder Rapids water coaster. It’s the largest in the world!<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<a href=\"https://thepmgrp.com\"><strong><u>About The PM Group:</u></strong></a> The PM Group was founded in 1988. Over the past 30 years, the agency has continued to grow and is currently listed as San Antonio’s Largest Advertising Agency by the <em>San Antonio Business Journal</em>. The PM Group’s client roster spans numerous industries including automotive, CPG, entertainment and sports marketing, legal, business services, non-profit, real estate and fitness. In addition, the agency hosts an annual Charity Gala every February that to date has raised over $2.5 million for local San Antonio area non-profit organizations in the last 15 years!  It is our way of giving back to the community that we so humbly serve.</p>\n","title":"IHOP Serves Up the Perfect Summer Fun Deal with Six Flags Fiesta Texas","seo":{"breadcrumbs":[{"text":"IHOP Serves Up the Perfect Summer Fun Deal with Six Flags Fiesta Texas","url":"/ihop-serves-perfect-summer-fun-deal-six-flags-fiesta-texas/"}],"title":"IHOP Serves Up the Perfect Summer Fun Deal with Fiesta Texas","metaDesc":"The IHOP Summer Fun Deal with Six Flags Fiesta Texas is in full swing and we’re sure you can’t wait to get your hands on this amazing deal...","focuskw":"deal","metaKeywords":"","metaRobotsNoindex":"index","metaRobotsNofollow":"follow","opengraphTitle":"IHOP Serves Up the Perfect Summer Fun Deal with Fiesta Texas","opengraphD